【Masamune】 I can't believe the dungeon was
created by Professor...

[Professor Melissa] I just used the dungeon that
was already there.

[Professor Melissa] Since I had information that
the four witches were infiltrating, I set up a
trap to lure them in.

[Professor Melissa] They are gathering this kind
of magic.
[Leon] As expected, the stamina magic...
[Principal] There is no such thing.
[Leon] Too bad...

[Principal] I thought we could catch her, being
from Caledonia, ourselves. But it seems like she
saw through all of our plans.

[Principal] For now, I'm glad that you all are
safe.
[Principal] Is Albert-kun alright as well?
【Masamune】 Your body seems to be fine, but...

【Sylvester von Weisshwaik】 I never expected that
you were Prince Albert.

[Skeleton Head] It's troublesome to be exposed as
a prince, you know.

[Skeleton Head] But now you know. There is no
prince being kept inside the castle.

[Skeleton Head] I was hiding my true identity and
having fun at the academy.

[Skeleton Head] There was never anyone that you
had to save from the beginning.
【Sylvester von Weisshwaik】 That's... a relief.

[Skeleton Head] Well, anyway, there was never any
treasure to begin with, so just do your best in
moderation.

[Skeleton Head] There is no aristocrat like the
Weisshwaik family, so...
【Sylvester von Weisshwaik】 Even so!

【Sylvester von Weisshwaik】 I want to change the
country!

【Sylvester von Weisshwaik】 I want to change the
suffocating world where someone who loves magic...
wants to change it!
[Skeleton Head] Hmm...!
【Masamune】 Oh...
[Leon] Finally, even Skeleton Head has spring...

【Sylvester von Weisshwaik】 That's why I will
continue to do my best. In order to acquire the
power to protect everyone.

[Skeleton Head] I-I see... In that case, do your
best.
【Sylvester von Weisshwaik】 Yes
[Skeleton Head] ...

[Skeleton Head] Are we going to be in a
relationship?
【Sylvester von Weisshwaik】 Huh? Why?

[Skeleton Head] Huh?! B-because earlier you said
you loved me...

【Sylvester von Weisshwaik】 That's about the
prince. You must be a man named Skeleton Head,
right?

【Sylvester von Weisshwaik】 I would never be in a
relationship with such a pervert.
[Skeleton Head] No way!

【Sylvester von Weisshwaik】 Your misunderstanding
is quite severe.

【Sylvester von Weisshwaik】 Don't talk to me too
much from now on.

【Sylvester von Weisshwaik】 Perverts are
contagious
[Skeleton Head] You're also a pervert!
[Sylvester von Weisshwaik] ...

【Sylvester von Weisshwaik】 You shouldn't be
disrespectful to the nobles of the von Weisshwaik
family.

[Skeleton Head] I'm telling you, there's no such
noble family! This is just an ordinary citizen!

【Masamune】 Ahaha, it seems like spring is still
far away.
~Emperor Leopold's Secret Treasure~ CLEAR
NF_NPC削除 1
【Masamune】 Is this the end...?
【Masamune】 No, that can't be true...
【Masamune】 Doesn't everyone realize?

【Masamune】 This disgusting magic power coming
from within...

【Masamune】 (They said this dungeon was made using
something that already existed)

【Masamune】 (If that's the case, it wouldn't be
strange for there to be hidden rooms that even the
professors haven't noticed)

【Masamune】 (But why am I the only one who
notices...)
